name: Pixo na Pracinha
description: "Pixo at the Square" is a 35mm photo taken in 2017, and a part of my personal exploration around brazilian culture & Pixo; as a "vehicle for the youth of the city to assert their existence and self-worth, and to do it loudly. As a social protest, Pichação is brutal, effective and pulls no punches." and it's interactions with the cityscape environment.
